text: Dr. Ambedkar Student Front of India (DASFI) is a student organization in India active in states of Madhya Pradesh, Haryana and Rajasthan. ==Campus activities== DASFI participates in elections at Kurukshetra University of Haryana. ==See also== *Birsa Ambedkar Phule Students' Association *Ambedkar Students' Association ==References== ==External links== * Category:Ambedkarite organisations Category:Student organisations in India Category:Student organizations established in 2012 Category:2012 establishments in India Category:Dalit politics
title: Dr. Ambedkar Student Front of India
